latestIgtvVideos.title: Lakmé X Born on Instagram
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Recreating Ananya Pandey's Runway Makeup Look using products sent to me by @lakmeindia in association with @creators @namratasoni @ananyapanday  #lakmexbornoninstagram 

This Soft Glam Pink Themed Look needs the following products- 
Step 1- wash your face using the Lakmé Absolute Perfect Radiance Skin Lightening Facewash (Rs. 160/-)
Step 2- Use the Lakmé 9to5 Matte Moist Mattifying Moisturizer .(Rs. 349/-) Dont forget to rub it in between your fingers before massaging it onto your skin. 

Step 3- Use the Lakmé 9to 5 CC cream in the shade- 02 Honey.(Rs.299/-) blend it using a Beauty blender. 

Step 4 - Next you can use the Lakme Absolute Brow pencil to do your brows. Don't apply force. just fill in the gaps. 

Step 5- Use the Lakmé Absolute Kohl ultimate - Silver Slate for your lower Water line. Rs.740/-
It opens up your eyes and defines it. 

Step 6- Use the Lakmé Absolute Infinity Eyeshadow palette - PINK PARADISE - (Rs.995/-)
I have used the Shades - Romance, Twilight, Paradise and Bark. The colors are really pigmented . Unleash your inner artist . 

Step 7 - I used the Lakmé Eyeconic Eyeliner (Rs.250/-) to make the perfect Wing . You will never need false lashes if you are using this product. 

step 8- Lakmé Eyeconic Curling Mascara(Rs. 440/-) has to be my favourite product. It instantly defines my lashes and makes them curly. 

Step 9- I've used the Matte Revolution Lip Colour in the shade-201 Insane Pink( Rs.800/-) as a blush and a lipstick. 

That's it guys ❤️❤️ That's my final Look. Do let me know if you Like it. 
❤️❤️✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨

Rajasthan - Jodhpur & Jaisalmer ❣️✨
Save this for your next trip - 
Jodhpur -The Blue city 💙
• Mehrangarh Fort - Jaswant Thada - 👑Breathtaking views 
• Umaid Bhavan Palace & Toorji ka Jhalra- Royal vibes ✨
•City Palace 
• Ghanta Ghar 
• Mandore Garden - Light and sound show🏞️

Cultural immersion - Meet artisans - gold and stone Philergy 🎹🎷
Shop Local🛍️ - Handicrafts, block print outfits and silver Jewellery 🥻

Food to try- Mirchi wada, Kadhi , Ghewar 🥮🥙♥️ 

Jaisalmer - The Golden City !!💛

Places to see- 🌄
•Jaisalmer Fort - A living fort ✨ Sonar Kella 

•Gadisar lake- perfect sunset spot 
•patwon ki haveli - Salim singh haveli - Nathmalji ki haveli ❣️👑
•Desert Adventure awaits !! 
Sam San dunes - jeep safari and Camel 🏜️Rides !🏝️
Star Gazing and Cultural performance.🌌
Enjoy Tent stays with Rajasthan food and Folk music. 🥁

Adventure - paragliding over the golden sands !!

Food to try- Lal mas , pyaz kachodi, dal baati churma , Ghotua Laddu .🍥🍡

Rajasthan is well connected by road , rail and Air .🛤️🧳🛬
 Jodhpur to Jaisalmer intercity -265km by road . Recommended - Travel by road for scenic views.

Tips- Book an auto 🛺/ 🚗car for a day .

Best season - October❄️ to February ☀️

Staying near the city centre enhances the experiences. 🌝

latestPosts.alt: A vibrant glimpse into Rajasthan’s royal charm — from Jodhpur’s iconic blue houses and the mighty Mehrangarh Fort to Jaisalmer’s golden sandstone walls glowing under the desert sun. The bustling streets of Jodhpur overflow with color, culture, and tradition, while Jaisalmer enchants with its vast Thar Desert, camel safaris, and magical sunset views. Folk dancers in bright costumes spin by a desert bonfire, bringing centuries-old traditions to life. This frame blends the cool blues of Jodhpur with the warm golds of Jaisalmer, capturing the rich heritage and visual poetry of Rajasthan in one unforgettable journey.
